
= Built-in Constants

data: ARGV
  type: Array

  The +Array+ object containing command line parameters. +ARGV[0]+ is a script file name. If Yog is invoked in an interactive mode, +ARGV+ becomes empty. With +__FILE__+ variables, you can make a special part in a script file\:

    if ARGV.get(0) == __FILE__
      # Here is executed when this file is invoked
    end

data: PATH_SEPARATOR
  type: String

  a path separator of directories

